'''钠离子电池'''（{{lang|en|Sodium-ion battery}}），是一种[[蓄電池|充电电池]]，主要依靠[[钠|钠]][[离子|离子]]在[[正極|正极]]和[[负极|负极]]之间移动来工作，与[[锂离子电池|锂离子电池]]相似。

==优势與劣勢==
由于钠离子比锂离子更大，所以重量和[[能量密度|能量密度]]不及鋰電，但当对材料性能要求不高时，钠离子电池是一种划算的替代品。<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Palomares | first1 = Veronica | display-authors = 1 | last2 = et al | year = 2012 | title = ''Na-ion batteries, recent advances and present challenges to become low cost energy storage systems''. In | url = | journal = [[Energy_and_Environmental_Science|Energy and Environmental Science]] | volume = 5 | issue = 3| pages = 5884–5901 | doi = 10.1039/c2ee02781j }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Pan | first1 = Huilin | display-authors = 1 | last2 = et al | year = 2013 | title = Room-temperature stationary sodium-ion batteries for large-scale electric energy storage | url = | journal = [[Energy_and_Environmental_Science|Energy and Environmental Science]] | volume = 6 | issue = 8| pages = 2338–2360 | doi = 10.1039/c3ee40847g }}</ref>因為钠离子电池使用的[[电极|电极]]材料主要是钠盐，相较于[[锂|锂]]盐而言储量更丰富，价格更低廉。<ref>https://wallstreetcn.com/articles/3631169</ref>2021年，寧德時代宣佈將會在年內投產钠离子电池，提供在有需要的使用場景中使用<ref>https://www.bnext.com.tw/article/63019/catl-batteries</ref>。
